# delete_irida_sequence_file
# delete a sequence file from a sample in IRIDA
#
# usage: delete_irida_sequence_file SAMPLE_ID FILE_ID
#
# NOTE: DELETE /api/samples/{id}/sequenceFiles/{fileId} is BROKEN on IRIDA 23.01.3.
# Returns HTTP 500 NullPointerException in SequencingObjectServiceImpl.readSequencingObjectForSample
# regardless of file type (fastq, fast5) and regardless of admin or non-admin token.
# See GitHub issue #4 for full stack trace.
# Files can be deleted via the IRIDA web UI.
